    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "John g. Woolley, the noted temper\nance lecturer and late candidate for\npresident on the prohibition ticket.\nwill arrive in the city tonight. and\nSunday afternoon at o'clock will\naddress a mass meeting for men in\nthe First Methodist church.\n\n\nAt s o'clock in the evening Mr.\nWoolley will deliver lecture at the\nAuditorium. An admission fee Of 10\ncents will be charged at the evening\nmeeting to meet expenses."
    }
